#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.LING.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.NORMAL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.LING.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.NORMAL"
msgid "My lantern, illuminating the path ahead."
msgstr "我的灯，照亮前方的道路。"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.LING.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.LOWFUEL
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.LING.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.LOWFUEL"
msgid "The light is fading, I need more nightmare fuel."
msgstr "光芒渐弱，需要更多噩梦燃料。"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.LING.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.LING.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.OUT"
