msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN"
msgid "Autumn's orphans cling to foreign boughs, frost-lit vigil keeping shadows at bay"
msgstr "落叶他乡树，寒灯独夜人"

