msgstr "光芒变得暗淡了。它需要更多燃料。"

#. STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.OUT
msgctxt "STRINGS.CHARACTERS.GENERIC.DESCRIBE.LING_LANTERN.OUT"
msgid "The lantern has gone out. It needs nightmare fuel to light again."
msgstr "灯已经熄灭了。需要噩梦燃料才能重新点亮。"

